86
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:37,760
It was delicious.

87
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,760
Don't worry about me.

88
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,800
Just rest well.

89
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,220
Rest assured.

90
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,970
