I think medication

116
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:36,390
is too slow.

117
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,640
Surgery is better,

118
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,480
right?

119
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:40,850
The risks
of this minimally invasive surgery

120
00:05:41,050 --> 00:05:42,800
are almost negligible.

121
00:05:42,970 --> 00:05:44,300
Our techniques

122
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:45,470
are quite mature,

123
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,600
so you don't need to worry.

124
00:05:49,010 --> 00:05:49,890
Alright,

125
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,300
let's do the surgery.

126
00:05:52,010 --> 00:05:52,890
How soon?

127
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:54,720
In two or three days. We'll hurry.

128
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,640
Thank you, Dr. Zhang.

129
00:05:56,970 --> 00:05:57,810
You're welcome.

130
00:05:58,260 --> 00:05:59,140
My pleasure.

131
00:06:00,010 --> 00:06:02,140
By the way, take Niannian home later

132
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:03,720
