152
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:38,470
They can keep each other company.

153
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,560
Right?

154
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:43,970
Thank you.

155
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,220
You've solved a big problem for us.

156
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,220
Thank you.

157
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,640
You're welcome.

158
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:55,930
Niannian,

159
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:57,850
I can tell you're really happy.

160
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,560
Not really,

161
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:03,300
but I'm a little excited.

162
00:07:04,890 --> 00:07:06,220
I just don't want to

163
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:09,110
trouble you and Mom

164
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,350
or make you worry.

165
00:07:12,470 --> 00:07:13,970
You're getting more sensible.

166
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,560
When you arrive,

167
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,720
remember to be polite.

168
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:19,220
Help with cleaning if you have time.

169
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,300
Is Jing'an's brother

170
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,600
a senior in high school?

171
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:24,890
Don't disturb his studies.

172
00:07:25,470 --> 00:07:27,720
I know, I won't bother him at all.

173
00:07:27,850 --> 00:07:29,010
Hurry up.

174
00:07:43,050 --> 00:07:44,850
Chen Jing'an will be here soon.

175
00:07:44,970 --> 00:07:46,140
I'll go cut some fruit.

176
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:47,470
There's a pineapple.

177
00:07:47,890 --> 00:07:48,730
No need.

178
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:51,220
