179
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,970
She doesn't eat it anymore.

180
00:07:55,850 --> 00:07:57,970
Then I'll see if there's anything else.

181
00:07:58,260 --> 00:07:59,140
Don't worry about her.

182
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,140
Coke from the fridge is fine.

183
00:08:02,850 --> 00:08:03,720
Okay.

184
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:21,390
Your dad didn't come up.

185
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,970
He went straight to the hospital.

186
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:50,430
(Cardiology Department)

187
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:56,390
Huiru,

188
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:57,310
have some water.

189
00:08:58,760 --> 00:08:59,890
Is Niannian settled in?

190
00:09:00,850 --> 00:09:01,720
Don't worry.

191
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:02,800
I drove her myself

192
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,260
to the Chen family's building.

193
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,470
Just downstairs?

194
00:09:05,810 --> 00:09:07,200
You didn't take her up?

195
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,450
Niannian's old enough now.

196
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:10,760
She can climb stairs on her own.

197
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:12,260
Just rest early.

198
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:13,300
Don't overthink it.

199
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:16,140
Remember to call her tomorrow.

200
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:18,220
