202
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:21,650
Okay, okay.

203
00:09:22,220 --> 00:09:23,470
Get some sleep.

204
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:24,940
You need proper rest

205
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:26,470
before the surgery.

206
