Both are.

208
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,850
Pick the hottest one.

209
00:10:12,970 --> 00:10:13,850
Lu Xiaojia.

210
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:17,050
You like the one who bathed in public?

211
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:27,600
Chen Changning,

212
00:10:27,970 --> 00:10:29,140
