213
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:33,890
The Lady of the Camellias?

214
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:35,720
What's fun with a tea-selling girl?

215
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,970
Come watch hot guys with me.

216
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,970
Not a tea-selling girl.

217
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,970
