262
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:11,970
not a cliché novel.

263
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:13,010
Not listening.

264
00:12:13,050 --> 00:12:14,350
You showered so long.

265
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:17,720
I'm sorry then.

266
00:12:18,050 --> 00:12:19,470
I'll shower faster next time.

267
00:12:19,930 --> 00:12:20,800
You're forgiven.

268
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:22,050
Watch this.

269
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:23,600
I can shower in just fifteen minutes.

270
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,640
You can start timing me.

271
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,890
Then go shower quickly.

272
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:27,430
I'm still waiting in line.

273
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:29,390
Keep waiting then.

274
00:12:39,890 --> 00:12:40,760
Niannian,

275
00:12:42,050 --> 00:12:43,430
she's always been careless.

276
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:45,180
